episodes.title: Cult of Death: Heaven's Gate
episodes.description: The true horror tale of a group of 39 people that committed suicide as part of the teachings of a cult that believed that they needed die in order to ascend to the next level up from humans.  Listen ad-free on Scary Plus. Get in touch at HorrorStory.com Find Edwin @edwincov on IG and Tiktok Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
